de.dfki.lt.mary.unitselection.featureprocessors
Class MaryGenericFeatureProcessors

java.lang.Object
  de.dfki.lt.mary.unitselection.featureprocessors.MaryGenericFeatureProcessors
Direct Known Subclasses:
MaryLanguageFeatureProcessors
public class MaryGenericFeatureProcessors
extends java.lang.Object

A collection of feature processors that operate on Target objects. Their names are all prefixed with "mary_" to make sure no confusion with the old FreeTTS feature processors occurs.

Author:
schroed
